            <lb/>aux fins de <choice><orig>recepuoyr</orig><reg>recepvoyr</reg></choice><expan>lesdits</expan><expan>supplians</expan> a veriffier par <unclear><expan>tables</expan></unclear><lb/>Que le droict du longey mentionne <expan>audit</expan> proces <expan>et</expan><choice><orig>leue</orig><reg>leve</reg></choice> par
