            <lb/><expan>que</expan><expan>aultres</expan> seigneurs voysins en recompence de ce <expan>que</expan><expan>combien</expan><lb/><expan>par</expan> les exporles les <expan>supplians</expan> ne soient tenuz lyer les
            <lb/>bledz ne iceulx porter en la maison <expan>dudit</expan> inthime ne
            <lb/>des <expan>autres</expan> seigneurs toutesfoys ils le font <expan>et</expan><expan>que</expan><expan>ledit</expan> droict
            <lb/>de longey a este <del>tolle <expan>et</expan> ce</del> introduict de tout temps <expan>et</expan><lb/>enciennette et <choice><orig>nest</orig><reg>n’est</reg></choice> memoyre du contrere / <expan>et</expan><expan>aultres</expan> pieces
            <lb/>et production <expan>desdites</expan><expan>parties</expan> faicte en la court
          </ab><ab><lb/>Il <expan>sera</expan> dict <expan>que</expan><expan>audit</expan> libel <choice><orig>na</orig><reg>n’a</reg></choice> aulcun faict <del>de</del><choice><orig>nouueau</orig><reg>nouveau</reg></choice><choice><orig>recepuable</orig><reg>recepvable</reg></choice><lb/>et sans <expan>autre</expan> esgard a <expan>ladite</expan><expan>requeste</expan> du dixneufiesme
            <lb/><choice><orig>feburier</orig><reg>febvrier</reg></choice><expan>ladite</expan> court a mis <expan>et</expan> met <choice><orig>lappel</orig><reg>l’appel</reg></choice><expan>et</expan> ce dont a este
            <lb/>appelle au neant Condampne <subst><del><expan>ledit</expan></del><add hand="#MainLDA" place="superposition"><expan>lesdits</expan></add></subst><expan>appellant</expan><add hand="#MainLDA">s</add><del><expan>et</expan><expan>consors</expan></del> bailler et
            <lb/>payer <expan>ausdits</expan> inthimes les droictz <choice><orig>dagriere</orig><reg>d’agriere</reg></choice> de tous les
            <lb/>grains <add hand="#MainLDA"><expan>et</expan></add> fruictz <choice><orig>prouen<subst><del>us</del><add hand="#MainLDA" place="superposition">ās</add></subst></orig><reg><orig>proven<subst><del>us</del><add hand="#MainLDA" place="superposition">ans</add></subst></orig></reg></choice> en leurs <expan>terres</expan><expan>et</expan> vignes <del>mentionnes</del><lb/><del><expan>audit</expan><expan>proces</expan></del> le tout <choice><orig>suyuant</orig><reg>suyvant</reg></choice> les exporles Et recongnoissances
            <lb/>produictes <expan>audit</expan> proces sans <expan>que</expan> de ceulx fruictz <expan>lesdits</expan><expan>appellans</expan><lb/>puissent prandre defalquer ou diminuer le droict du dixain 
          
          
          
